{"tid":527371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又有！韓國民間組織發起集體訴訟　控告蘋果減慢iPhone運行速度","createTime":"2018-01-12T14:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T15:02:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afcb86e8b99192f6ad1af767e63a3cac3e46bf4a","tid":527371,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司早前承認減慢舊款iPhone運行速度，惹來用家不滿，韓國有民間組織周四（11日）代表150名iPhone用戶，向首爾中央地方法院向蘋果公司及其韓國子公司提出控訴，要求公司向<span style=\"color: red;\">每人賠償220萬韓圜（約1.6萬港元）。</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司在事發後，減價為顧客更換電池，惟仍未能平息用家不滿，民間組織領袖高桂鉉（Go Gye-hyeon，音譯）指：「蘋果違反商業道德，並且成為全球焦點，在這情況下，韓國消費者不應留在原地，所以我們提出集體訴訟。」<br />\n<br />\n今次風波引起各地顧客不滿，在韓國這類訴訟案還陸續有來，有當地公司指會向蘋果發出集體訴訟，而原告人數目更加多達35萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/149131/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F-%E6%8E%A7%E5%91%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%B8%9B%E6%85%A2iPhone%E9%81%8B%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F149131%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25A8%259F-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%2585%25A2iPhone%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%25BA%25A6&d=KUovSg7Sk1ulPtZPieiY3nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e302e72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/149131/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F-%E6%8E%A7%E5%91%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%B8%9B%E6%85%A2iPhone%E9%81%8B%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6</a>"},{"pid":"4ec55591d6de3bf3053f745b686e60a9b7a59bc5","tid":527371,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/l